100% Happiness Guarantee
All of our services come with our exclusive 21 Day Happiness Guarantee. If for any reason you are less than 100% satisfied, Carpet Masters will promptly return and re-clean any portion of your job. If you are still less than satisfied, we will refund the cost of that portion of your job.

A Few of our Recent Projects

Chris Muetterties, Owner

Chris moved to Arnold, CA in 1970 where he attended Hazel Fischer Elementary School and Bret Harte High School. After graduation he married his wife Carah of 26 years and raised their 3 adult children in Angels Camp, CA. Chris and Carah have a passion for all the beauty the Gold Country has to offer. In 1999 Chris started Carpet Masters Cleaning & Restoration and loves to solve customers problems. Chris’ desire to always provide the best service and results to his clients has him constantly attending schools and trade shows in a never ending search of improving the quality of service his company provides. Carpet Masters Cleaning & Restoration has invested in the very best equipment the industry has in an effort to give you the very best results imaginable, each and every time.

Tyler Cones, Lead Technician

Tyler was raised in Calaveras County and graduated from Bret Harte High School in 2016. Tyler is a quiet, hard working young man who loves animals and woodworking. Tyler loves to make things on his lathe and if you need something custom, just ask him. Next time you see Tyler you need to ask about his collection of cat T-shirts and more than likely he will be wearing one under his work shirt.

What Our customers say
